            <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
             <a href="/topic/extreme-weather-5wx">
              Extreme weather
             </a>
            </h5>
           </div>
           <h3 class="_2XVos _1rgER" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/national/nsw/thousands-could-be-evacuated-as-western-sydney-residents-forced-to-flee-20210321-p57cpw.html">
             Thousands more could be evacuated as western Sydney residents forced to flee
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            Almost 140 schools have closed, roads and bridges have been cut off, the vaccine rollout has been delayed in parts of Sydney and NSW because of the extreme weather.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="_2GjOK">
          <div class="_15r1L KrNcv _2uY5P _2A036" data-an-position="2" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">

              Bitter dispute between NSW ministers over overflowing dam
             </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
             Since the heavy rain hit, Warragambas spillway has released 450 gigalitres a day. Sydney Harbour holds about 500 gigalitres.
            </p>

          <a href="/politics">
           Politics
           <svg height="1em" viewbox="0 0 32 32" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">

        <div>
         <div class="_1c5ra">

           <figure class="XmCQH" data-pb-type="im">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/politics/federal/angry-nats-push-for-travel-industry-job-retention-scheme-20210321-p57cmd.html" tabindex="-1">
